0.02d0      vecy    - k_y, 1/cm
0.02d0      vecz    - k_z, 1/cm
8000        ndisp   - number of points for dispersion curves    
80000      npoi    - number of points for Runge-Kutta integration
100.d0      x_in    - inner boundary for x=R variable, cm
300.d0      x_out   - outer boundary for x=R variable, cm
299.d0      x_A     - antenna position over x, cm
175.d0      xmid    - localiation center of the additional damping term, cm
3.0d0       sigma   - Gaussian width of the additional damping term, cm
0.5       ampnu0  - amplitude of the damping term for solution 0, N_A^2 units
0.25      ampnu1  - amplitude of the damping term for solution 1, N_A^2 units
1.0       ampnu2  - amplitude of the damping term for solution 2, N_A^2 units
50         nx_harm - number of Fourier harmonics in x-expansion
12.0         delx    - width of the conversion layer, cm
0.3         xmargin - cut-off point of the localizer, in delx units
0.20        delta_band - half-width of the minimization region, in delx units
1           iswitch_cold_warm - permittivity: 1 - cold plasma, 2 - warm plasma

